Administrable, IComponent, IDataProcessor
public class MapScriptProcessor
extends ScriptProcessor

ScriptProcessor which executes scripts in the context of a Map data record. Scripts may reference fields in the record directly by name. If new fields are added then use oa_data.put() (substituting an alternate dataBinding if it has been changed)

public java.lang.Object[] process(java.lang.Object data)
Process a Map data item. It bind each key->value pair in the supplied map into the scriptEngine. Actual processing is delegated to the superclass.
